## üß© CI/CD Integration

### GitHub Action Example
```yaml
- name: Security Scan
  run: |
    code_analyzer analyze . \
      --format sarif \
      --output results.sarif
      
- name: Upload SARIF
  uses: github/codeql-action/upload-sarif@v2
  with:
    sarif_file: results.sarif
```

